TEST process_todo_created_event

RECEIVE HTTP:POST /api/v1/notifications/events
WITH {{payloads/todo_created_event.yaml}}

EXPECT HTTP:GET http://user-service.local/api/v1/users/42
HEADERS
  Authorization: Bearer service_token_xyz789
RETURNS {{payloads/user_42.yaml}}

EXPECT WRITE:POSTGRESQL notifications
WITH {{payloads/notification_insert.yaml}}

RESPOND HTTP:200
